=Episode 8=

3
00:01:02,540 --> 00:01:03,420
Commander.

4
00:01:07,220 --> 00:01:08,140
Commander.

5
00:01:13,860 --> 00:01:14,780
Commander.

6
00:01:16,300 --> 00:01:17,700
You scared me to death.

7
00:01:17,860 --> 00:01:19,020
What took you so long?

8
00:01:24,420 --> 00:01:28,020
I thought you'd abandoned me.

9
00:01:29,860 --> 00:01:31,620
Did I ever say that?

10
00:01:32,860 --> 00:01:36,460
I thought you
only cared about your wife.

11
00:01:39,020 --> 00:01:40,380
Why bring her up?

12
00:01:42,860 --> 00:01:44,220
She won't even let me touch her.

13
00:01:45,740 --> 00:01:47,219
Unlike you.

14
00:01:47,220 --> 00:01:48,260
Wait.

15
00:01:48,780 --> 00:01:50,860
Weren't you two
all lovey dovey after the wedding?

16
00:01:50,940 --> 00:01:53,940
- How have you never touched her?
- I don't like women who talk too much.

17
00:02:26,660 --> 00:02:27,460
Commander.

18
00:02:29,420 --> 00:02:30,620
Gu Nianchi.

19
00:02:47,460 --> 00:02:48,500
Put the gun down.

20
00:03:09,780 --> 00:03:10,660
Gu Nianchi!

21
00:03:28,860 --> 00:03:31,020
Why do you feel like
a completely different person today?

22
00:03:31,340 --> 00:03:33,180
Yesterday, you barely spared me a glance,

23
00:03:33,540 --> 00:03:36,260
and now you're doting on me like this.

24
00:03:38,380 --> 00:03:39,300
Yesterday?

25
00:03:39,820 --> 00:03:40,740
Yeah.

26
00:03:41,380 --> 00:03:44,820
Yesterday, you even told me to get lost.

27
00:03:49,320 --> 00:03:51,280
You went to
the Commander's Residence yesterday?

28
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:52,700
Yeah.

29
00:03:52,900 --> 00:03:54,420
Weren't you there too?

30
00:03:58,220 --> 00:03:59,619
Didn't I tell you before?

31
00:03:59,620 --> 00:04:03,020
Without my permission, you're not allowed
to come looking for me at the residence.

32
00:04:05,340 --> 00:04:06,820
Why can't you ever listen?

33
00:04:07,420 --> 00:04:09,500
I just wanted to teach her a lesson.

34
00:04:10,300 --> 00:04:11,300
But...

35
00:04:11,820 --> 00:04:12,979
After today,

36
00:04:12,980 --> 00:04:14,100
she'll be dead.

37
00:04:15,060 --> 00:04:16,420
Don't worry, Commander.

38
00:04:16,420 --> 00:04:19,480
You won't have to keep pretending for
the sake of the marriage alliance anymore.

39
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:21,019
She's already your wife.

40
00:04:21,020 --> 00:04:24,340
Even if she dies, her property will still
end up with the Commander's Residence.

41
00:04:26,700 --> 00:04:27,659
Idiot.

42
00:04:27,660 --> 00:04:28,860
You hit me?

43
00:04:30,820 --> 00:04:31,940
Idiot.

44
00:04:38,220 --> 00:04:39,220
Commander.

45
00:04:39,540 --> 00:04:42,660
I kept you around because at least you

46
00:04:42,860 --> 00:04:45,060
were pretty to look at.

47
00:04:45,980 --> 00:04:47,339
I never expected you

48
00:04:47,340 --> 00:04:49,780
