49
00:04:50,660 --> 00:04:51,660
Commander.

50
00:04:54,220 --> 00:04:55,340
Where is she?

51
00:04:55,580 --> 00:04:56,500
She...

52
00:04:57,660 --> 00:05:00,020
She's at the warehouse in West City.

53
00:05:37,860 --> 00:05:38,980
